Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒問題嗎 扇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我有責任讓大家避難
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我對不起你們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你們捲入Freyja所支配的戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托瓦密艦隊被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰計畫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰計畫繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Avalon就這樣後退
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持和Damocles的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各部隊以波狀攻擊 讓Damocles繼續發射Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣簡單就…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉 下一次發射準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Damocles的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰術沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 只要進入腹地 就用不了Freyja了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Blaze Luminous?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼巨大的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Damocles原本就是為了掌握 絕對制空權而製造的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓它再繼續提升高度 我們會束手無策的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 能突破那防守嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在試 但是跟對方功率差太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這狀態下應該發射不了Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這邊的攻擊沒用 就跟旁觀沒兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界只能在Freyja壓倒性的恐怖中沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是所謂和平狀態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殘存兵力以Avalon為中心集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連同人質對Damocles發動突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你既然回來了 就說明已經有眉目了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過之後還要看陛下和朱雀君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈澤爾 你打算連同人質一起消滅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在黑騎士團已經敗退了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還沒輸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就等十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才十分鐘?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是已經取得反擊位置了才聯繫我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 十分鐘是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把下一彈發射前所必須的十分鐘 賣了個高價啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是做好戰後處理的準備而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是說黑騎士團已經沒用了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為集合體的軍事力量有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 利瓦爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們學生會成員以世界為敵作戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是挖苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為我沒能保護妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經很努力了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從後面?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑騎士團?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要親手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繞過來了嗎 星刻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不讓你擊落Avalon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星刻 在此止步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這違背情理之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樞木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種狀態竟能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已醜陋到捨棄國家 只執著於地位了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想要什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只期望明天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你期望的那是什麼明天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 真不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一浮空裝置受損
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受損率75%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會墜落嗎 這Avalon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著慢著慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 給我們的因緣做個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是有志氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒趕上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是讓他們進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成白刃戰就有勝機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壓制動力控制和通信系統 去救人質
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臣遵旨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撐到這裡就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本艦就此降落太平洋上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們去執行Apate．Aletheia任務
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你們的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡能發射嗎 Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經張開了Blaze Luminous 到臨界點之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.19,0:06:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 雖然是讓黑騎士團消失的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我個人的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是尤菲米婭殿下的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我必須去做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那個的最終程式 必須輸入環境資料才能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經夠了 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從剛才的話中我已理解了你的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧你能協助我這尤菲的仇敵 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會原諒ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許一輩子都不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 另一方面 我必須找到自己的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C. 你沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真稀奇 你在擔心我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是重要的戰力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我來取那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 麻煩你護衛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許要親手攻擊娜娜莉也不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她成為零之鎮魂曲的障礙也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修 你不恨我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為GEASS 大大改變了你的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像你啊 明明是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C. 因為有你給我的GEASS…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有你 我才能邁出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後的事 一切都由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次碰到你這樣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我來阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡交給我 你去Damocles
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 對手是紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很開心 你在擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去 然後回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要給我笑容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 約定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一步棋 無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵方Knightmare編隊正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先鋒是蜃氣樓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將Freyja發射口的Blaze Luminous部份解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄準目標改為蜃氣樓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修 最後要捨命一擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真難看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標變更完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉 這樣就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 修奈澤爾皇兄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Blaze Luminous解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 輸入資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Freyja每一時刻結構都會發生變化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要破壞對應其結構的反應 Freyja的臨界反應就會停止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 必須在離爆炸約19秒時 把現場環境資料登錄程式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而就算程式完成 實行時間也只有0.04秒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原理上應該是可行的 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤菲米婭殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,19秒和0.04秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然準備了這種玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在 沖進去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突破Blaze了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,α3有敵機侵入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鑰匙 Damocles的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,δ區通信斷絕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第六浮空裝置控制室被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈澤爾殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起啊 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然逼我用最後的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要用那個?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 Damocles 已成為捕捉魯魯修他們的牢籠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們脫離後 用Freyja將Damocles整個消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美的棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會喜歡嗎 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Damocles要是上了衛星軌道 就算是Lancelot也束手無策了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要贏就必須壓制修奈澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在分析內部構造
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:11:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密碼的阻截…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉諾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修 我不承認你的布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 這力量是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉諾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修 你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還有必須打倒的敵人和必須拯救的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉諾 無論如何都要一戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 為了我心中要守護的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要守護的東西 我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守護?什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈澤爾在管制指令層嗎 還是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第7步驟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Freyja起爆位置 變更為Damocles本體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Damocles和Freyja 終究都是機械
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再造就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 托洛莫機關沒這種餘力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅森堡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在全世界都是魯魯修的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是消滅魯魯修的系統 各種組織都會樂意製造Freyja給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是恐怖主義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該也問問娜娜莉殿下的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒必要吧 誘餌的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道您要拋棄她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界和平與一條生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然悲哀 但這是不能比較的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鑰匙 鑰匙在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須阻止哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是橋頭堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在閣下作戰成功之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭現在的魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Knight Of Six
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是相稱的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不為國家 不為復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有絲毫野心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有戰鬥理由的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別攪進來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理由我有 就是約定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說你喜歡魯魯修?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過想結束經驗的積累了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也會說人話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不虧是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮 是你贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然還會在意勝負…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鑰匙 鑰匙在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須阻止哥哥才行 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即將出發
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和胡爾特葛籣卿匯合地點是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正等著你呢 修奈澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 被將軍的是我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能告訴我嗎 為什麼會知道我的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是策略 我所看穿的是你的本質
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本質?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒打算獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱禁城的對局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑騎士團的政變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總是站在不會輸的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你就知道我要放棄Damocles?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈澤爾 這次你一定得輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是 殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洪古從第三通道壓制艦橋 各國代表的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天子陛下 您平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他們救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星刻大人 我們是你們的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們背叛了魯魯修?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是被威脅的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 既然魯魯修已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不再是獨裁者的意義上 應該能信任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 決戰似乎縮小到Damocles內部了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇先生…事務總長也在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 他們都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果 皇兄沒有殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇兄沒有執著的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若生而逢時 應能成為不凡的王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有看穿這點 是我太愚蠢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還這樣稱呼我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想提個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想用Damocles來掌控世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想創造大家都期望的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使無視人的本質?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們見解相異
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想將世界固定在今日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 沒有變化的日常稱不上生存
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是經驗而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:18:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 經驗的累積就是知識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然很優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過優秀而看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 皇帝查爾斯追求的是昨日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你追求的是今日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我想要的是明日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日或許會比今日更糟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 會更好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為無論要花多少時間 人都會不斷追求幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而這分明就是欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢至極
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不過是感情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名為希望和夢想的不可靠的虛構
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在皇族的符號之下 俯視世界的你的極限
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我見過無數次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與不幸抗爭的人 和追求未來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都期望著幸福 不斷掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GEASS和面具 其根源就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自相矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直否定他人意志的你 事到如今卻要肯定人的意志的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了 殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過 你也會被Freyja消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們的生命 換來世界的和平…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 送你一句話 侍奉ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你從一開始就不是要殺我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何沒能察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是看穿了修奈澤爾思考的錄影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽憑您的吩咐 ZERO大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈澤爾 認定自己會被殺的想法 招致了你的敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 你的故事已經完結了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能再活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有否定我存在的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈澤爾殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對自己的生命都無所依戀的人竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是GEASS的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 至少在最後 對我也施以GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪特哈爾特 你沒有施加GEASS的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 修奈澤爾 首先解除Damocles的自爆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 Freyja的控制開關在娜娜莉手上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論機體如何強化 你都贏不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真敢說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是結果 吉諾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我的任務已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Blaze Luminous系統?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 吉諾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 看來到了結的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為我們不同的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.63,0:21:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的目的是Damocles的鑰匙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那對你來說太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再避開視線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打破了那傢伙的GEASS?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 也會對我用GEASS嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.34,0:23:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也許從那天開始 我就一直迷茫著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.95,0:23:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,厭倦了這毫無改變的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是就是無法對自己撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 名字也 經歷也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,得到的力量也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.67,0:24:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都是讓我得到真實 所需要的路標而已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.96,0:24:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,也許我一直在追求的正是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.99,0:24:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
